# Harness Skills

This repository uses Harness. Available skills can be invoked by reading
the SKILL.md in .agents/skills/<name>/.

## Available Skills

### harness-advanced-elicitation
Push the LLM to reconsider, refine, and improve its recent output. Use when user asks for deeper critique or mentions a known deeper critique method, e.g. socratic, first principles, pre-mortem, red team.
Invoke: Read `.agents/skills/harness-advanced-elicitation/SKILL.md`

